---
title: Mexican Pork Mince & Bean Chilli with Jacket Potatoes & Tomato Ensalada
description: Our pork mince is taken to a new level with our Mexican Fiesta spice blend. While it comes with a spicy
warning, you can tailor it to your tastebuds by adding as little (or as much!) as you’d like. Cool things down with some
plant-based mayo.
